<tt>Thu Nov 20 10:20:05 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Heads Up, Super John!<br><br>
Maybe we can't get our old buddies back.. but the prospects of getting some new ones here are great.<br><br>
Never abandon your love and respect for those who gave all and perished, but try and focus on guys like yourself who gave all and managed to limp away.<br><br>
Try and stop your weeping, sobbing, protestations of gratitude and intense prideful joy in know that you were not a dumb Maureen.  We all share that sense of extreme elation (except for one unfortunate!) Instead, do something constructive..like petition the Department of Defense to change their gaudy uniforms, so they too can lift their peeled heads with pride.  It's a disgusting revolting job to have to protect and rescue Moreens.. but somebody has to do it!<br><br>
To illustrate the fact that we can't always have what we want most in life, I leave you with this famous quote:<br><br>
       &quot;Gee, wish I were like Mustang Two Four!&quot;<br><br>
                            Chesty Puller<br><br>
